{"tid":1418603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【收到風】九月一會成立獨立委員會降溫","createTime":"2019-08-05T19:21:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:44:24.000Z","uid":271068,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"35395a114c82f4c7bd486f89cdb0a9251e4e6d7c","tid":1418603,"uid":271068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:21:08.000Z","msg":"有人同你講，林鄭想捱到九月一，先考慮到市民的意見，我們決定成立咩會，有咩咩咩各選一位人做（可能係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">梁振英</span></span>加王永平或者陳方安生），屆時你又被代表了，再加上開學日，莘莘學子第一次返大學，萬種徬徨，記㧅田的召集人呢就會成為左代表暫定你，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支持梁振英</span></span>做獨立委員會調查嘅聯席主席<br />\n<br />\n無論咩方式<br />\n<br />\n無大台 是唯一威脅到政府的戰術<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不要民間記者招待會</span></span><br />\n林鄭要聽聲音自己落街聽<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民間記招召集人會代你同意梁振英成為獨立調查委員會主席</span></span>"},{"pid":"8031685ced4d2bbd9e39f396aa5309f6d6d8817c","tid":1418603,"uid":48611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:29:37.000Z","msg":"收到風你老母死撚左"},{"pid":"c46ec292fbe03119d23bdd368f73b5f788fa039e","tid":1418603,"uid":271068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8031685ced4d2bbd9e39f396aa5309f6d6d8817c","tid":1418603,"uid":48611,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T19:29:37.000Z","msg":"收到風你老母死撚左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T06:44:24.000Z","msg":"pish"}]}